STRAITS OF FLORIDA.
CUBA TO FLORIDA.
DISTRESS SIGNAL RECEIVED ON 406 MHZ FROM 45 FOOT
S/V MOON BEAM, CREAM HULL, FIVE PERSONS ON BOARD,
BETWEEN HAVANA (23-08N 082-23W) AND KEY WEST
(24-33N 081-47W). VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED
TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE.
REPORTS TO RCC MIAMI, PHONE: 305 415 6800,
E-MAIL: RCCMIAMI@USCG.MIL.
